      "text": "Jocelyn Nungaray should be a teenager now.\n\nInstead, she was sexually assaulted and brutally murdered in June 2024 by two Venezuelan nationals in the country illegally.\n\nThanks to ICE’s VOICE Office, immigration crime victims and their families are not alone.\n\nOur skilled liaisons:\n \n—Help victims understand the immigration enforcement and removal process\n—Provide victims with access to social service professionals and resources\n—Help victims receive custody status updates on criminal aliens \n\nCall 855-48-VOICE, Monday-Friday 8 A.M. to 8 P.M. ET or visit us online at https://t.co/Eh8BbBROsn.\n\nCelebrating the one-year anniversary on April 9 of the Trump Administration's VOICE Office relaunch.",
